CANADA
Our Canadian operations mainly consist of an oil sands development in the Athabasca Region of northeastern Alberta and a liquids-
rich unconventional play in western Canada. In 2018, operations in Canada contributed 8 percent of our worldwide liquids
production and less than 1 percent of our natural gas production.
 
