Table of Contents
EUROPE AND NORTH AFRICA
The Europe and North Africa segment consists of operations and exploration activities in Norway, the United Kingdom and Libya.
In 2018, operations in Europe and North Africa contributed 19 percent of our worldwide liquids production and 18 percent of
natural gas production.
