During 2013, a lease of a semi-submersible floating production system (FPS) commenced for the Gumusut development, located in
Malaysia, in which we are a co-venturer. The FPS lease provides for an initial noncancelable term of 15 years, a subsequent 5-year
cancelable term with no required lease payments, and an
 
