earlier of five years after the grant date of the award or the date the employee becomes eligible for retirement. For employees
eligible for retirement by or shortly after the grant date, we recognize compensation expense over the period beginning on the date
of authorization and ending on the date of grant. Otherwise, we recognize compensation expense beginning on the grant date and
ending on
 
