Contract Liabilities from Contracts with Customers
We have entered into contractual arrangements where we license proprietary technology to customers related to the optimization
process for operating LNG plants. The agreements typically provide for negotiated payments to be made at stated milestones. The
payments are not directly related to our performance under the contract and are recorded as deferred revenue to be recognized as
revenue when the customer can utilize and benefit from their right to use the license. Payments are received in installments over the
construction period.
 
